OL,6,FToday, on White Ribbon day, the
OL,7,Fcampaign that encourages men to hold
OL,8,Fthemselves accountable, council
OL,9,Fleaders in Portsmouth pledged to make
OL,10,Fsure women and girls feel safe in the
OL,11,Fcity.
