OL,7,Fsuffered months of abuse at the hands
OL,8,Fof her husband.
OL,10,FShe said: "When he took the knife and
OL,11,Fwhen he came to kill me, then I
OL,12,Fthought, this person doesn't love me
OL,13,Fanymore"
OL,15,F"I lost my life. I lost my future. I
